{"name": "django-surface-theme", "metadata": {"name": "django-surface-theme", "version": "0.0.13", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Software Development", "Topic :: Software Development :: User Interfaces"], "home_page": "https://github.com/surface-security/django-surface-theme", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["Django", "django-jsoneditor"], "summary": "Open-source Surface template with improved functionality", "upload_time": 1734439241}, "documentation": ["# django-surface-theme\n\nSurface theme is built on top of [Django Dashboard Atlantis Dark](https://appseed.us/admin-dashboards/django-dashboard-atlantis-dark).\n\n[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-surface-theme.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-surface-theme)\n\n## Surface Theme variables\n\nDefine custom title in `urls.py`:\n```\nadmin.site.site_title = \"Surface Security\"\n```\n\nDefine side menu navigation items by adding the following variable in `settings.py`:\n```\nSURFACE_MENU_ITEMS = [\n    {'label': ('Organisation'), 'icon': 'fas fa-building', 'items':[\n        {'name': 'auth.user'}\n    ]},\n    {'label': ('Organisation'), 'app_label': 'auth', 'icon': 'fas fa-building', 'items':[\n        {'name': 'user', 'label': 'Custom Label'},\n        {'url': 'https://example.com', 'url_blank': True, 'label': 'Custom URL'}\n    ]},\n]\n```\n\nDefine home links and items by adding the following variable in `settings.py`:\n```\nSURFACE_LINKS_ITEMS = [\n    {'label': ('Examples'), 'items':[\n        {'url': 'https://example.com', 'url_blank': True, 'name': 'Example.com'}\n    ]}\n]\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "theme.templatetags.surface_the